(2336, 181, 'i want to develop the mobile app for kids', 'Thank you for sharing your project idea! Developing a mobile app for kids sounds like an exciting project.\n\nTo help me understand your vision better, could you please provide some more details?\n1.  **What is the primary purpose or goal of this app?** For example, is it for educational games, interactive storytelling, creative activities, or something else entirely?\n2.  **What age group are you targeting for the children who will use the app?** (e.g., toddlers, preschoolers, elementary school children, pre-teens?)\n3.  **What kind of key features or content do you envision for the app?** (e.g., mini-games, animated stories, drawing tools, quizzes, video playback, parental control features?)\n4.  **Will the app need to be available on both iOS (Apple devices) and Android devices, or just one platform?**\n\nDo you have any more requirements to add, or are you ready to complete the requirements? Please write \'complete requirement\' if you\'re done.', '2025-11-17 05:30:45'),
