(2684, 184, 'i need it for iphones only , both functions browse products and make purchases', 'Thank you for clarifying that you need an iPhone-only app with product browsing and purchasing functions. To ensure we capture all details for this, please consider the following:\n\n1.  **Target iOS Version**: For the iPhone app, do you have a target iOS version range in mind (e.g., iOS 15 and above, or broader compatibility)? Are there any specific iPhone models you want to prioritize?\n2.  **Product Information Display**: When users browse products, what kind of product information should be displayed (e.g., images, descriptions, prices, reviews, stock availability)? Will there be categories, search functionality, or filtering options?\n3.  **User Accounts & Checkout**: For the purchasing functionality, will users need to create accounts, or can they check out as guests? Will there be a shopping cart feature?\n4.  **Payment Methods**: What payment methods do you intend to support (e.g., credit cards, Apple Pay, PayPal, other digital wallets)?\n5.  **Order Management**: How will order management work? Do you need features like order history, shipping address management, or tracking for users within the app?\n6.  **Product Data Source**: Where will the product data (inventory, prices, descriptions) for the app come from? Do you have an existing e-commerce platform or database that the app needs to integrate with, or will this be a new system?\n\nDo you have any more requirements to add, or are you ready to complete the requirements? Please write \'complete requirement\' if you\'re done.', '2025-11-24 09:02:39');
